longBusinessSummary: Adtraction Group AB provides advertising services in Europe. It develops and operates a platform, which connects advertisers that want to increase their sales with various partners, activities, brands, products, and services, such as digital magazines, influencers, bloggers, forums, mobile apps, and price comparison sites. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
